# [parser-skip]   message: "Three or more related blocked issues is a cascade, not a backlog. The correct response is a single meta-issue for coordination, not more individual issues."
# [parser-skip] 
# [parser-skip] constraint lesson_2026_03_praxis_business_cascade_3:
# [parser-skip]   severity: error
